New version of my old map zm_beach_city. [Here you come to the old version](http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/170370 "")

I added a 3D skybox and im working on the custom soundscape.txt for a nice 
ambient. Some secrets are the same but the way to get in there are new. Overall
I added some other new secrets and much new spots. I didnt remove any spots
of the old version i just make them better and add much new spots.

I think the map is done in few days.

The Download will be the old map!
